    <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">τὸ</supplied>ν τράχηλον αὐτοῦ <supplied reason="lost">τοῦ</supplied> πρεσβυτέρου ἀπόστημα καὶ ἐξ αὐτοῦ <unclear reason="undefined">ἀ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">πέθνῃσκ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined">εν</unclear>, περὶ γὰρ Ἡρα<unclear reason="undefined">κ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">λ</supplied>είου οὔδε <subst><add place="inline">ἤμην</add><del rend="corrected"><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>μην</del></subst> ἐκε<unclear reason="undefined">ῖ</unclear> οὔδε <unclear reason="undefined">ο</unclear>ἶδα. <foreign lang="la">Vir inlustris <expan>com<ex>es</ex></expan> <expan>m<ex>ilitum</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>ixit</ex></expan>:</foreign> εἰ βούλονται οἱ ἑστῶτες 

